    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Ankle osteoarthritis with adequate bone stock

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Mental or physical inability to consent or answer pain questions, pre-operative or
             peri-operative morbidity impairing mobility, pre-operative opioid therapy,
             non-steroidal anti-inflammatory drugs or steroids within 24 hours before skin
             incision, kidney or liver dysfunction, morbid obesity, smoking, significant bony
             deformity, significant loss of bone stock or diabetes with sensory changes will be
             cause for exclusion.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
